'''奧蒂河'''（{{lang-en|Oti River}}，又名Pendjari）是[[西非|西非]]的河流，發源自[[布基納法索|布基納法索]]，最後注入[[沃爾特水庫|沃爾特水庫]]。奧蒂河是[[貝寧|貝寧]]與布基納法索接壤邊境的一部分，也成為[[多哥|多哥]]和[[加納|加納]]的部分邊境<ref name="Rivers and Lakes">{{Cite web|url=http://www.countrystudies.us/ghana/30.htm|title=Ghana - Rivers and Lakes|website=www.countrystudies.us|access-date=2017-08-17|archive-date=2016-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161103012341/http://countrystudies.us/ghana/30.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。奧蒂河流經貝南的[[彭賈里國家公園|彭賈里國家公園]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pendjari.net/en/ |title=Parc National de la Pendjari |access-date=2016-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170714032607/http://www.pendjari.net/en/ |archive-date=2017-07-14 |url-status=dead }}</ref>，以及多哥的[[凱蘭國家公園|凱蘭國家公園]]<ref name=Hughes>{{cite book |author=Hughes, R.H. |title=A Directory of African Wetlands |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=VLjafeXa3gMC&pg=PA443 |year=1992 |publisher=IUCN |isbn=978-2-88032-949-5 |pages=443–447 |access-date=2022-02-01 |archive-date=2017-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170501000407/https://books.google.com/books?id=VLjafeXa3gMC |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

